# TreeOS Land . AGPL-3.0 . https://treeos.ai . Tabor Holly

# What never crosses the seam into the public repo.

# The I-Am's identity at the host's level. Carries the JWT signing
# secret. If committed, anyone with the repo can sign as me. .env.example
# is the public shape; .env is the private instance.
.env

# Operational state that belongs to this specific running I-Am, not
# to the kernel's shape. Each land's .land/ is its own.
.story

.test
# localStore: CAS bytes for matter content + resource files.
/store

legacySeed



.shared

# Rust port: ignore only build output + tooling noise, NOT the source.
# Keep Cargo.toml / Cargo.lock / src/ (the actual port); drop target/ and backups.
/seed/target/
/seed/**/target/
/seed/**/*.rs.bk

# Old experiments kept for reference, not for shipping.
.oldExtensions

site/
cli/

# Rust napi addon build artifact (platform-specific; rebuild via cargo)
seed/treehash-node/*.node
seed/treehash-node/target/
